 – Cambridge University Press Bookshop|https://www.cambridgebookshop.co.uk/products/the-trial-of-the-templars|# The Trial of the Templars  Author(s): Malcolm Barber ISBN: 9781107645769 Publication Date: 29/03/2012 Pages: 408 Format: Paperback  £15.99 GBP  £15.99 GBP  Quantity  ...    Malcolm Barber's classic The Trial of the Templars recounts the dramatic demise of this elite military force in the fourteenth century. Having fought against Islam in the crusades in the East for nearly two centuries, in October 1307 the members of this respected Order were arrested on the order of Philip IV, King of France and charged with serious heresies, including homosexuality and the denial of Christ. Finding resonances between the fourteenth-century trial and contemporary events, Barber's
